---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Larry Quan — qualified electrician and lead foreman. Domestic, commercial and industrial electrical work in Kilkenny.">
	<section class="py-20 md:py-28">
		<div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="max-w-2xl">
				<p class="font-heading text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-amber-600">Who we are</p>
				<h1 class="font-heading mt-2 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 md:text-5xl">About Quan Electrical</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="mt-10 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-xl">
				<img
					src="https://picsum.photos/seed/quan-about/1200/600"
					alt="Quan Electrical — Kilkenny"
					width={1200}
					height={600}
					class="aspect-[2/1] w-full object-cover"
					loading="eager"
					decoding="async"
				/>
			</div>
			<div class="prose prose-slate prose-lg mt-14 max-w-none">
				<p class="text-xl leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
					Quan Electrical provides professional electrical services across Kilkenny and the southeast. Led by Larry Quan, we deliver domestic rewires, commercial installations, EV charging points, and more — all carried out by qualified electricians and fully certified.
				</p>
				<h2 class="font-heading mt-14 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Experience</h2>
				<p class="text-slate-600">
					Larry has worked as a lead foreman on domestic, commercial, and industrial projects and has experience overseeing sites across Ireland. He has worked with various companies and brings that same standard of quality and reliability to every job we take on.
				</p>
				<h2 class="font-heading mt-10 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">What we offer</h2>
				<p class="text-slate-600">
					From full house rewires and consumer unit upgrades to shop and office fit-outs, EV charger installation, and security lighting — we give clear quotes, tidy work, and proper certification. We're happy to work with homeowners, landlords, and contractors.
				</p>
				<h2 class="font-heading mt-10 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Service area</h2>
				<p class="text-slate-600">
					We're based in Kilkenny and cover Kilkenny City, Castlecomer, Thomastown, Callan, and the surrounding counties. Get in touch for a free, no-obligation quote.
				</p>
			</div>
			<p class="mt-14">
				<a href="/contact" class="inline-flex rounded-xl bg-amber-500 px-8 py-4 font-heading font-semibold text-slate-900 shadow-sm transition hover:bg-amber-400">Get in touch</a>
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
